Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种…应该叫做『Koper转』吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Kopernikanische回转』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}（德）Kopernikanische回转：与历来哲学相反 客观从属主观的观点回转
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\1cH000000\fad(100,500)}美川煌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚？神乐坂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  对方好像是营销部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前碰到她时  还说没有正在交往的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真信了她的话啊  春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是故意不让人知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  被骗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下可不是笑的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我就不可能隐瞒起来么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不会撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不渴望结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相亲之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为嘛…现在还是看小说比较有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说工作是编辑  结果还不是只被差使复印东西啦倒茶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和OL没什么区别啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  这才是我工作的第三年嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西  这个每张复印十份  麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是第三年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西你很喜欢美川煌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是他的大FAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中时还给他写了慕名信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌的担当(编辑)  从今天起由你来做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法了 上吧 弥次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 喜多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你们所愿 抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}小心点  我现在很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『弥次喜多』么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部电影里那个时代男人间肝胆相照的友情  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没有做作的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何贵干  妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  其实有本想借的书(恶搞自谦语)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有了喜欢的男生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是什么类型的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小夏想看书的时候就是有了喜欢的人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看同一本书对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏总是喜欢上很聪明的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反…反正就是喜欢和自己个性相反的类型啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  是什么书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人虽然跟我是同班同学  已经是4年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  成为美川煌老师的担当了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  第一次当作家的担当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  本来就是他的FAN  紧张死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野岛  要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话跟我说？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  一副幸福得要死的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是有不幸的存在  幸福才格外显眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么不幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为不幸的根源还有资格问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊  我还不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  居然无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是这次的收信人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁啊  难得看到文伽有那种反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着时和他有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着时  我对他开了枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饮料没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶点没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸和姐姐上班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈外出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静  夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是关于文歌的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为这事  他怎么会找我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  你不是去上班了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是闹钟停了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把闹钟按了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  直接去美川煌老师那里  还赶得上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…提早了一点来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  好一个知书达礼的文科少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家的夏香就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢惹哭她  我会好好教训你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  先进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在住院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他在家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是绕段路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…很重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于美川的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说被文歌拒绝过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是打算再次告白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是  想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见到美川了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不应该见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为美川她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在沉睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前开始就一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是见到了  或许吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是偶然相似的别的什么人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么跟文伽长得一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  我的另一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「另一部分」？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪击父亲和这件事难道有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么美川会对自己的父亲开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有苏醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是正在KISS什么的  真的抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记去煌老师家的地图了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能用手机发过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我房间里有扫瞄仪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会用什么扫瞄仪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏  谢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐是美川煌的担当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近刚成为的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才发去的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去见美川煌亲自确认美川的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然美川无法苏醒  知道真相的就只有美川煌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(284,80)}美川煌老师家的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(284,147)}无边无际的银色之路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(594,80)}在森林里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(554,173)}石桥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(554,240)}街道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(338,213)}地藏菩萨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(338,280)}汽车站
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(513,413)}海鸥市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无边无际的…银色之路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 千惠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌的新作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都四年没出了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说得事不关己似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是出了  肯定可以卖80万册
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担当交给年轻的社员了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个据说很没用的…没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫「谁知道啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正她本来就很没用  用坏了也不可惜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个  初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我  我是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭田桥出版第一编辑部的葛西春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了  新的担当  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美川煌  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我要去见美川煌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我想见你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮  都是玻璃笔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起金属制的笔  用这些我能写得更美些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到亮处去聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃是美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀着的时间的连续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸其中  才是无上的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃的…闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌文字处理机啊圆珠笔啊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它们不美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我把原稿拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天在展示会上展示的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请过目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  还没倒茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有上好的香草茶  稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}光明中的闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然听说作家中有很多怪人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是因为我是从来不读书的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  文歌对于自己一直被看作美川煌的女儿感到厌倦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我对演歌没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说错了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后  开始经常和文歌说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌是个少言寡语的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天都待在学校的保健室里  她的事具体我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只是」？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只问过我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我「夏香的父亲是什么样的人？」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  原来那么大受好评吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人吃惊  一处重写的地方都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些连草稿都没打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然老师很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为构思阶段花了大量的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  能否让我参观下您的工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作室？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么美丽的原稿  是在哪写成的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作室很脏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思见人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是我失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明预报是10%的可能性的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是太阳雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明出太阳了  还下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨  闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明出太阳了  明明出太阳了  明明出太阳了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  小心感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳雨  太阳雨哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有过的呢  这种电影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  停了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好一场阻碍前进的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么抽象模糊的目的地  叫我到哪找美川煌的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}无边无际的银色之路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不渴望结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银色之路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来尺寸很合身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这是谁的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来猜猜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下了  我收下了  我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慕名信吗  真怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也跟老师您写过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了回信  感激不已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是进了公司才知道  那是编辑回的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  信能让我看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种字  是中学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  煌老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫银色的Njord
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}Njord：出自北欧神话 神分为两个部族 以主神奥丁(Odin)为首领的阿萨神族(Aesir)\N以及以大海之神尼约德(Njord)为首领的华纳神族(Vanir)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我读了老师所有的书
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数次地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽而残酷  最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后的世界如同冰雪的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有生命  没有色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫  细菌  没有任何污垢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终极洁净的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死  并不悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清静  美丽的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直认为只有黑暗和恐惧的死后的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种…应该叫做『Koper转』吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Kopernikanische回转』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从死后的世界寄来的信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以称为死后文
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  找到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神圣的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…打火机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  要烧掉那封信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是慕名信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差劲的字  依赖的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性的决定  自我陶醉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有品位的信封
